          <h2>I Spent a Decade Watching Agencies Get It Wrong. So I Built Something Different.</h2>
          <p>I've worked inside the digital marketing industry for nearly ten years. I've helped hundreds of agencies with their operations and interviewed nine agency owners a week for the last six months. I've watched practices pour thousands into marketing that never moved the needle, because their agency didn't understand their world.</p>
